node.text:
Where we start a haircut suggests where we want the control or which direction we want the length or weight to travel.
With short hair I feel if we start at the side the shape looks graduated and if we start from the back the shape looks more layered or flatter.
So when you look at a short haircut decide on its characteristics, does the shape look layered or graduated?
This decision will help you in deciding where to start the haircut.

.
It is our hope to aid anyone wanting to learn and develop but my not have the time! “I can’t take time out of the salon at the minute” believe me I’ve been there,
When I retrained at 34 years old I didn’t have the time or the money to afford the training I wanted and needed, I used online education to totally change the direction of my career.
I would use it whilst a client was being shampooed or if I had 10 mins I would make sure I was always learning.
